{"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cleanup","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lean.Meta.CollectFVars","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Clear"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L61-L64","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup.collectUsed","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup.collectUsed","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L55-L59","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup.collectProps","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup.collectProps","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L48-L53","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup.collectPropsStep","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup.collectPropsStep","doc":"We include `p` in the used-set, if `p` is a proposition that contains a `x` that is in the used-set. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L42-L45","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup.addUsedFVar","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup.addUsedFVar","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L36-L40","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup.addDeps","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup.addDeps","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L31-L34","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup.addUsedFVars","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup.addUsedFVars","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.lean#L18-L64","name":"Lean.Meta.cleanup","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cleanup.html#Lean.Meta.cleanup","doc":"Auxiliary tactic for cleaning the local context. It removes local declarations (aka hypotheses) that are *not* relevant.\nWe say a variable `x` is \"relevant\" if\n- It occurs in the target type, or\n- There is a relevant variable `y` that depends on `x`, or\n- The type of `x` is a proposition and it depends on a relevant variable `y`.\n"}]}